Base, a layer-2 solution by Coinbase, is designed to make blockchain accessible, offering fast, low-cost transactions and tools like Coinbase Paymaster to sponsor gas fees for users. Its Builder Network provides community forums, gas credits, and investment opportunities for early-stage projects.

Talent Protocol supports creators by connecting them with rewards and opportunities to showcase their work. By partnering with Base, Talent is helping creators leverage the Base ecosystem to build and monetize their projects, from digital art to mini-apps.

Together, Base and Talent Protocol are fostering a vibrant creator economy, as highlighted by posts on X emphasizing Baseâ€™s support for creators and its focus on virality as a new distribution model.

